教你一下把
Location a = 设定位置;
Location b = 玩家位置;
double x2 = (a.getX()-b.getX())*(a.getX()-b.getX());
double y2 = (a.getY()-b.getY())*(a.getY()-b.getY());
double z2 = (a.getZ()-b.getZ())*(a.getZ()-b.getZ());
double distance = Math.sqrt(x2+y2+z2);


if(distance<设定距离）{
BossBar bar = Bukkit.createBossBar("名字",org.bukkit.boss.BarColor.BLUE（蓝色）,org.bukkit.boss.BarStyle.SEGMENTED_20（20段血条）,org.bukkit.boss.BarFlag.CREATE_FOG（迷雾）);

bar.addPlayer(玩家）；
bar.setProgress(distance/设定距离)；
//这里设定血条进度懒得算了自己想吧复制代码

血条类型枚举org.bukkit.boss.BarStyle.SOLID
//不分段
org.bukkit.boss.BarStyle.SEGMENTED_10
//10段
org.bukkit.boss.BarStyle.SEGMENTED_12
//12段
org.bukkit.boss.BarStyle.SEGMENTED_20
//20段
